description: This file declares external API functions for an Atom Table Object used in the Advanced Networking Service Container (ANSC). It contains function prototypes for creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization of the atom table, but no implementation details or class definitions.

methods.name: AnscCreateAtomTable
methods.description: Creates a new atom table object with provided container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscAtoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Atom Table object with the specified context handles.

methods.name: AnscAtoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified atom table object.

methods.name: AnscAtoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the atom table.
